The paper deals with image denoising, which is a common problem in computer vision and image processing. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves optimization techniques and noise estimation, which are relevant to cs.MM (Multimedia). Additionally, the paper uses mathematical tools such as singular value decomposition, which is related to cs.IT (Information Theory). The proposed modifications in the algorithm also involve machine learning techniques, which are relevant to cs.LG (Machine Learning).
